BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: TorontoBabel Language Exchange
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/
UID:event_312578562@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260402T030656Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T230000
SUMMARY:Language Exchange & Social Event @ Madison Ave Pub by Toronto Babe
 l
DESCRIPTION:TorontoBabel: Toronto's International Language Exchange\nWe’
 re back for another night of great conversation\, community\, and global c
 onnections. Whether you want to practice English\, learn a new language\, 
 or simply make new friends from around the world\, this is the place to be
 !\n\n✨ **What to Expect:**\n✅ Language Exchange 💬 – chat in Frenc
 h\, Spanish\, Korean\, Japanese\, and more!\n✅ Live Music & Resident DJ 
 🎵 – groove while you mingle\n✅ Fun Board Games 🎲 – challenge a
  new friend\n✅ Arts & Crafts 🎨 – get creative\n✅ Make New Friends
  🗣️ – the more\, the merrier!\n\n📍 14 Madison Ave\, Toronto\, ON
  M5R 2S1\n🕖 7:00 PM – 11:00 PM\n\nCome solo or bring a friend—eithe
 r way\, you’ll leave with new connections\, good laughs\, and even bette
 r vibes 💬✨🫶\n\n💵 $5 Entry Fee at the Door\nThis helps cover mee
 tup essentials like games\, name tags\, stickers\, and all the little thin
 gs that make our events magical ✨\n\n**CONTACT:** Terry (Organizer)\n
 📲 E-transfer also available: tmg8@wealthsimple.me\n🔗 Meetup: [https:
 //www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel](https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel)\n📘 
 Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/groups/torontobabel](https://www.faceb
 ook.com/groups/torontobabel)\n💬 WhatsApp: [https://chat.whatsapp.com/EY
 MdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt7](https://chat.whatsapp.com/EYMdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt7)\n
 📸 Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/t.o.babel](https://www.instagra
 m.com/t.o.babel)\n\n👉 Check out our calendar to see what other events w
 e have coming up and to RSVP:\n[https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel/#calen
 dar](https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel/#calendar)\n\n**Note:** Toronto B
 abel is a friendly\, welcoming\, and safe space for all attendees. This is
  a language-focused event and not a dating or matchmaking event. Any form 
 of harassment or inappropriate behavior will not be tolerated. If you expe
 rience or witness any issues\, please inform one of the organizers.\n\n#To
 rontoBabel #LanguageExchange #TorontoEvents #ToDoToronto #LearnEnglish
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/events/312578562/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251226T014839Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251226T014839Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
